code: @Override public void writeTo(final StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     out.writeEnum(this). }
public static SortBy readFromStream(final StreamInput in) throws IOException {     return in.readEnum(SortBy.class). }
public static SortBy resolve(final String str) {     Objects.requireNonNull(str, "Input string is null").     return valueOf(str.toUpperCase(Locale.ROOT)). }
